没错。

7
00:00:13,960 --> 00:00:19,520
We are listening in as somebody gets a little bit of trouble from their boss for being a
我们将听到有人因为项目进度有点落后而被老板训斥。

8
00:00:19,520 --> 00:00:21,280
bit late on a project.
有点晚了。

